@TechMovesLogistics.Api_HostAddress = https://localhost:7216

### GET all contracts
GET {{TechMovesLogistics.Api_HostAddress}}/api/contracts
Accept: application/json

###

### GET contracts filtered by status
GET {{TechMovesLogistics.Api_HostAddress}}/api/contracts?status=Active
Accept: application/json

###

### POST create contract (use a valid clientId from your database)
POST {{TechMovesLogistics.Api_HostAddress}}/api/contracts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "clientId": 1,
  "startDate": "2026-01-01",
  "endDate": "2026-12-31",
  "status": "Draft",
  "serviceLevel": "Premium Freight"
}

###

### PATCH update contract status (cannot test in browser address bar — use Send Request here)
PATCH {{TechMovesLogistics.Api_HostAddress}}/api/contracts/1/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Active"
}

###
